---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Wellness Recommendations — Moulin à Rêves" description="Trusted local yoga teachers, massage therapists, and beauty practitioners near Moulin à Rêves. We share contacts; you book directly.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero" style="height: 60vh;">
    <div class="hero__image">
      <img src="/images/wellness-riverside-massage.webp" alt="Massage table set on the lawn beside the stream and mill house at Moulin à Rêves" />
    </div>
    <div class="hero__overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero__content">
      <h1 class="hero__title" data-i18n="wellness.hero.title">Wellness</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro -->
  <section class="section--tight">
    <div class="container--narrow text-center fade-in">
      <h2 data-i18n="wellness.intro.heading">Bien-Être</h2>
      <p data-i18n="wellness.intro.subhead" class="serif-italic" style="margin-top: 6px; font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.4rem);">The Art of Relaxation</p>
      <p data-i18n="wellness.intro.text" style="margin-top: 20px;">At Moulin à Rêves, well-being comes naturally. The gardens, the river, and the slower rhythm of French country life create an atmosphere of beauty, tranquility, and restoration. For those seeking a little extra indulgence, we are happy to connect you with trusted local practitioners who can enhance your stay with services at the estate.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Yoga -->
  <section class="section--tight fade-in">
    <div class="split">
      <div class="split__image">
        <img src="/images/wellness-yoga-tree.webp" alt="Tree pose during a yoga session on the lawn at Moulin à Rêves" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="split__body">
        <h2 data-i18n="wellness.yoga.heading">Yoga on the Lawn</h2>
        <p data-i18n="wellness.yoga.p1">Practice beside the river, in the gym, or in La Grange. Private yoga instructors can be arranged for individuals or groups. Ten yoga mats are available for guest use.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Massage -->
  <section id="massage" class="section--tight fade-in" style="scroll-margin-top: 96px;">
    <div class="split split--reverse">
      <div class="split__body">
        <h2 data-i18n="wellness.massage.heading">Massage</h2>
        <p data-i18n="wellness.massage.p1">Enjoy a relaxing massage in the privacy of your guest room or outdoors beside the river, surrounded by the beauty of the estate.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="split__image">
        <img src="/images/wellness-massage-willow.webp" alt="Massage table on the lawn beneath the willow, with the painted bridge beyond, at Moulin à Rêves" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Beauty -->
  <section class="section--tight fade-in">
    <div class="split">
      <div class="split__image">
        <img src="/images/wellness-beauty.webp" alt="Bright tile bathroom at Moulin à Rêves" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="split__body">
        <h2 data-i18n="wellness.beauty.heading">Beauty Treatments</h2>
        <p data-i18n="wellness.beauty.p1">Facials, manicures, pedicures, and beauty treatments can be arranged at Moulin à Rêves. For guests who prefer to venture into town, Méréville hosts two beauty salons offering a full range of services.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Le Temps de Vivre -->
  <section class="section--tight">
    <div class="container--narrow text-center fade-in">
      <h2 data-i18n="wellness.temps.heading">Le Temps de Vivre</h2>
      <p data-i18n-html="wellness.temps.p1" style="margin-top: 20px;">The French have a phrase, <span class="serif-italic">le temps de vivre</span> — the time to live. It is the pleasure of slowing down, savoring the moment, and enjoying life without hurry.</p>
      <p data-i18n="wellness.temps.p2" style="margin-top: 16px;">Whether it's a morning yoga class, an afternoon massage, or simply a quiet moment in the garden, Moulin à Rêves offers space to restore, reconnect, and enjoy the pleasures of the present moment.</p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn--green" data-i18n="wellness.cta.button" style="margin-top: 28px;">Join us</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .section--tight { padding-top: 56px; padding-bottom: 56px; }
  </style>

</BaseLayout>
